---
tags: [ packaging ]
---
# To install sdk:
curl -s "https://get.sdkman.io" | bash

# To list available sdks:
sdk list

# To list available sdk versions:
sdk list <sdk>

# To see current installed sdks:
sdk current

# To install sdk:
sdk install <sdk> <version>

# To use sdk version:
sdk use <sdk> <version>

# To set a sdk version permanently:
sdk default <sdk> <version>
